---
title: Mexican Bean Chilli & Tomato Salsa with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: Say hello to the best bean in town, nutrient-packed black beans. They are wholesome and filling and go perfectly in a bowl with garlic rice and a tomato-cucumber salsa. Now cook it up in a fiery sauce to drive home those mouth-watering flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67a55bbed9ab91e06051fd56-aa155fb9.jpeg
